      "code": "PX161601",
      "abbreviation": "PX161601",
      "description": "This protocol is a proxy-administered personal health record from the American Health Information Management Association (AHIMA). The parent or guardian is asked to provide details on the child in the following categories: Birth, Health Log, Allergies/Drug Sensitivities, Infectious Disease, and Immu",
